correctness.rationale: The extraction is largely incorrect and not schema-compliant. Numerous fields are missing, null, or speculative, violating both the schema (types and required fields) and the no-empty-values rule. Key issues: (1) Unsupported/incorrect parameters: deposition temperature set to 200 °C (not reported in article); aldMethod fixed to TALD for InOx/GaOx/ZnO without evidence; coReactant=H2O for IGZO sub-cycles is not stated (H2O is only specified for Al2O3 passivation). (2) Required numeric fields left null: pressure.quantityValue.numericValue, multiple growthPerCycle values, nucleationPeriod, dosingTime and purgeTime numeric values, flowRates, numberofSubcycles counts, uniformity variation, conformality aspect ratio, filmComposition elemental concentration numeric values, roughness, filmDensity; device onOffRatio; many fields contain 'Not Found' or None, violating schema types and task constraints. (3) Invalid objects: plasmaPower set to null (type mismatch); reactantSelection placeholders ('Not Found') for precursors, carrierGas, purgingGas with no traceability. (4) SupercycleDesign is speculative and incomplete (counts are null). (5) Only a few values are correct and traceable: substrate=Si wafer; IGZO film thickness 10 nm; device metrics μ_FE=25.3 cm^2/V·s, V_TH=0.14 V, SS=63.3 mV/dec (from Fig. 1(d)). Nearly all other properties need removal or correction to align with the article and schema; if not reported, they should be omitted rather than filled with placeholders/nulls.

completeness.rationale: Largely incomplete and non-compliant. (1) Missing processes: the article describes multiple ALD steps (IGZO channel deposition; SiO2 passivation processes A and B; Al2O3 passivation using TMA/H2O) but only one IGZO process is extracted. Separate structured processes for SiO2 (process A and B) and Al2O3 passivation are absent. (2) Non-traceable/incorrect values: deposition temperature (200 °C), number of cycles (10), aldMethod=TALD, IGZO co-reactant=H2O, supercycle sequence and counts are not reported in the article; “saturation=True” and “amorphous” phase are also unsubstantiated. (3) Schema violations and nulls: many required numeric fields are null (pressure.quantityValue.numericValue, growth-per-cycle values, dosingTime/purgeTime/flowRates numericValue, nucleationPeriod, uniformity variation, conformality aspect ratio, elemental concentration, roughness, film density, on/off ratio), and plasmaPower is null; these violate the schema’s numeric requirements. (4) Limited traceability: only a few values match the article (substrate=Si wafer; IGZO film thickness=10 nm; device metrics μFE=25.3 cm2/V·s, VTH=0.14 V, SS=63.3 mV). To improve, add separate ALD process entries for SiO2 (A and B) and Al2O3 (TMA/H2O) passivation, remove or correct unsubstantiated fields (temperature, aldMethod, co-reactant, supercycle design, cycles), and populate required numeric parameters without nulls or omit optional sections if not reported.
